  m_text: "Congratulations on making it through your first day! Crustacean Corporation
    is excited to assist you in restoring this station to its former glory.\n\nWe
    have partnered with the station to start a new shuttle route that exclusively
    transports Crustacean Corporation\u2019s guests and employees to the worksites.
    Shuttle passengers will present their exclusive shuttle tickets when arriving. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
